WEBVTT

00:00:01.075 --> 00:00:04.056
Moishe Geguzhinskis, VILNUS, LITVA.

00:00:08.155 --> 00:00:10.330
kent forzetsn.

00:00:10.137 --> 00:00:13.067
yo, di lage in lager far di yidn

00:00:13.562 --> 00:00:17.972
iz geven a zeyer a shvere. fun tog tsu tog hot flegt zikh farerger- farergern di lage.

00:00:17.972 --> 00:00:21.774
vos vayter flegt men gebn vos veyniker tsum esn un vos mer arbetn.

00:00:23.181 --> 00:00:29.244
ikh hob alts getrakht vi azoy vel ikh gefinen mayn foter.

00:00:29.244 --> 00:00:32.962
mayn foter iz geblibn in a tsveytn lager. in lager fir, hob ikh gehert.

00:00:33.357 --> 00:00:36.619
vi azoy vel ikh im gefinen, efsher efsher vet er vet mir oyskumen

00:00:36.619 --> 00:00:42.480
az a a a a UNK a poshet tsu gefinen a veg vi tsum vi zikh mit im tsu zen.

00:00:43.650 --> 00:00:49.646
do in a tog iz gekumen tsu geyn in lager a komisye fun doktoyrim, fun fun daytshe doktoyrim,

00:00:49.646 --> 00:00:56.470
un zey hobn opgesh- opgeteylt shvakhere mentshn shvakhere UNK fun geto fun fun lager

00:00:56.577 --> 00:00:59.051
oyf tsu shikn in lager fir.

00:01:01.622 --> 00:01:11.336
ikh hob zikh arayngeshtelt in rey un ikh hob un m'hot mir fartribn arayngetribn in lager fir. emes zogndik ikh bin far dem tsu ersht in lager dray ikh bin oykh geven a kurtse tsayt.

00:01:11.443 --> 00:01:14.943
un fun dortn hot men undz avekgefirt in lager fir. der lager fir iz geven

00:01:14.943 --> 00:01:17.743
eyner fun di shreklekhste lagern in in in yener gegnt

00:01:17.743 --> 00:01:22.168
fun Dakhau. dos iz geven mentshn hobn dortn nit gearbet, mentshn hobn dortn zenen nor gelegn

00:01:22.168 --> 00:01:24.618
in di barakn un gevart oyfn toyt.

00:01:24.707 --> 00:01:29.699
vayl der esn iz dortn geven zeyer a sh- zeyer a shlekhter,

00:01:29.699 --> 00:01:32.903
un mentshn flegn oysgeyn fun hunger.

00:01:33.162 --> 00:01:36.277
in barak zenen mir geven bay fuftsik mentshn arayngeshtupt.

00:01:37.279 --> 00:01:43.112
der in yeder barak iz geven a u- a elterer, ikh gedenk a belgisher yid.

00:01:43.776 --> 00:01:55.886
er iz geven, er hot geheysn Meyshe Bronfman. er flegt undz teyln

00:01:56.010 --> 00:02:03.243
lign- di ligndike oyf di be- oyf di kanare flegt er undz teyln yedn tog dem mitog, azoy tsu zogn, dem yu- dem yushnik.

00:02:04.060 --> 00:02:09.509
di lage iz geven a shvere, un in der ershter rey hob ikh getrakht

00:02:09.509 --> 00:02:12.634
vi tsu gefinen mayn foter. ikh bin durkhgegangen

00:02:12.634 --> 00:02:16.509
durkh ale barakn, ikh hob gezukht, ikh hob nokhgefregt bay di mentshn, efsher hobn zey gekent aza min mentsh

00:02:16.509 --> 00:02:19.334
vi Aron Geguzhinski, efsher hobn zey getrofn vu nit iz.

00:02:19.334 --> 00:02:23.159
un eyner a yid, a elterer yid shoyn, kam kam, hot mir

00:02:23.159 --> 00:02:25.309
ongevizn, zogt er, veyst, in dem barak

00:02:25.309 --> 00:02:30.334
ligt a kranker yid, a mentsh a krank, un er ge- kam vos er leb- er lebt shoyn oys.

00:02:31.060 --> 00:02:33.551
mir dukht az er hey- mir dukht az er heyst Aron.

00:02:34.317 --> 00:02:36.437
ot o, zog ikh, dos iz mistome mayn foter.

00:02:37.202 --> 00:02:47.085
ikh bin arayn in dem barak un ikh hob gegebn a kuk, s'zenen gelegn oyf di bara- in di oyf di oyf di nares oysgetsoygn halb lebedike mentshn.

00:02:47.918 --> 00:02:52.603
ikh hob gezukht tsvishn zey mayn foter, un ikh hob gefunen er ligt, ikh hob im gefunen.

00:02:52.643 --> 00:02:54.217
ikh hob zikh mit im tsekusht.

00:02:54.217 --> 00:02:57.752
er iz geven bavaksn, er iz geven alt gevorn un krank.

00:02:57.752 --> 00:03:07.253
er hot mir derzen, hot er hot er mir gezogt, "veyst Meyshele, mir dukht az mir veln zikh shoyn mer, du zest mir du zest mir du zest mir shoyn tsum letstn mol.

00:03:07.253 --> 00:03:08.533
ikh vel nit oyshaltn."

00:03:09.805 --> 00:03:16.566
ikh hob zikh mit gezegnt, vayl ikh hob gemuzt geyn tsurik in mayn barak, dortn flegt men yedn tog UNK kontrolirn.

00:03:17.871 --> 00:03:21.915
oyf morgn bin ikh vider avekgelofn vider dortn tsum foter maynem,

00:03:21.938 --> 00:03:24.260
ikh hob gezen az der mentsh shtarbt avek.

00:03:24.621 --> 00:03:26.674
azoy iz er oysgegangen bay mir oyf di hent.

00:03:29.127 --> 00:03:34.048
in dem lager fir flegn yedn tog shtarbn

00:03:34.797 --> 00:03:38.065
bay fertsik fuftsik protsent fun di on- fun di fun di lager mentshn.

00:03:38.323 --> 00:03:40.629
vayl fun hun- zey flegn shtarbn fun hunger.

00:03:40.635 --> 00:03:44.606
in dem barak vu ikh hob gelebt zenen geven

00:03:44.606 --> 00:03:51.125
flegn yedn tog shtarbn a helft, bay fuftsik protsent. in der fri flegn mir oyfshteyn flegn mir zen zen di zen lign lebn zikh toyte mentshn.

00:03:54.912 --> 00:03:57.659
s'iz shoyn geven di letste s- s'shoyn geven friling's tsayt.

00:03:57.659 --> 00:03:59.389
nor mentshn hobn nokh alts geshpirt

00:03:59.389 --> 00:04:03.798
az zey veln zikh efsher a mol bafrayen, efsher veln zey kenen a mol nokh zen di heym.

00:04:04.969 --> 00:04:11.122
eygntlekh hob ikh getrofn dortn dem Karal Klabin, Klabin dem shokhn maynem.

00:04:11.719 --> 00:04:19.661
dos heyst dem zun Klabin. der alter zun, dem altn Klabin hob ikh nit gezen. ikh hob getrofn dem Love Love Klabin vos iz geven a sportler in der tsayt fun farn krig,

00:04:20.173 --> 00:04:22.499
hot er lib UNK lib UNK raytn oyf ferd,

00:04:22.499 --> 00:04:27.103
un a sheyner yung, ikh hob im gezen un ikh hob im gezen er iz gelegn oyfn dakh

00:04:27.160 --> 00:04:29.595
a naketer, ayngeviklt in a koldere.

00:04:29.595 --> 00:04:36.181
un er hot zikh gevaremt mit der frilinker zun velkhe hot zikh shoyn dan bavizn, in april monat iz shoyn dos geven.

00:04:36.677 --> 00:04:38.561
ikh bin tsugegangen tsu im, zog ikh, Lova,

00:04:38.955 --> 00:04:44.732
vos makhstu? vi geyt d- zogt er tsu mir, freg nit, mir iz shlekht, zogt er. ikh vel mistome nit oyshaltn.

00:04:44.732 --> 00:04:46.729
mayn foter, zogt er, iz nit lang geshtorbn,

00:04:48.473 --> 00:04:52.753
un ikh, zogt er, bin, zest dokh vi ikh ze oys, ikh bin shoyn oykh keyn keyn mentsh nit.

00:04:54.261 --> 00:04:55.827
ikh hob zikh mit im azoy gezegnt,

00:04:55.827 --> 00:05:00.161
un ikh hob farshtanen az der mentsh far di mentshn blaybn do getseylte teg.

00:05:02.935 --> 00:05:07.180
s'iz shoyn geven di letste teg fun april monat.

00:05:09.870 --> 00:05:12.024
vos vayter iz gevorn erger un erger.

00:05:12.756 --> 00:05:15.349
di daytshn flegn undz veynik vo- vos veyniker gebn esn.

00:05:16.013 --> 00:05:24.512
un m'hot ongehoybn tsu reydn vegn dem az m'vet aroys- m'vet aroysfirn dem lager di mentshn di lebedike gebli- di lebn geblibene mentshn vet men aroysfirn fun lager un m'vet zey avekshikn

00:05:24.906 --> 00:05:27.937
in tif in Daytshla- in in in mayrev in Daytshland.

00:05:29.462 --> 00:05:33.019
emesn glaykh hot zikh bavizn daytshe komandes, m'hot flegt araynkumen

00:05:33.019 --> 00:05:34.867
araynkhapn zikh in di barakn,

00:05:34.867 --> 00:05:40.256
oyszukhn di mer veyniker mer shtarkere mentshn velkhe kenen nokh shteyn oyf di fis,

00:05:40.465 --> 00:05:45.099
vayle di ligedike velkhe zenen shoyn di farkhaleshte mentshn flegn zey shoyn nit tshepenen.

00:05:45.392 --> 00:05:48.153
un m'hot zey m'hot aroysgetribn oyfn oyfn hoyf,

00:05:49.257 --> 00:05:52.744
un oyfn hoyf zenen geshtanen kares azelkhene,

00:05:54.336 --> 00:05:58.585
geleygt a vegele ongelodn tsu di kar- di furn,

00:05:58.585 --> 00:06:02.126
un gesh- un m'hot gefirt tsum tsum tsum ayznban linye.

00:06:02.757 --> 00:06:05.310
di ershte teg hob ikh zikh bahaltn. ikh hob nit gevolt.

00:06:05.310 --> 00:06:08.454
ikh hob farshtanen m'firt efsher tsum tsu mistome tsum toyt. m'vet

00:06:09.068 --> 00:06:15.002
efsher vet mir gelingen zikh gelingen zikh fun dest vegn bahaltn, un ikh vel blaybn fun dest vegn lebn.

00:06:16.341 --> 00:06:22.410
nor do hot men mir alts eyns gekhapt. untern nare bin ikh gelegn, hot men mir gekhapt, m'hot mir aroysgetsoygn far di fis,

00:06:23.327 --> 00:06:28.535
mir un maynem a khaver fun Holand, a yid- a yid- a yidisher yingl fun Holand.

00:06:28.710 --> 00:06:30.560
der nomen gedenk ikh shoyn nit.

00:06:32.406 --> 00:06:36.618
un m'hot undz ara- avekgezetst a- arayn- aray- avekgefirt tsu der ayznban linye.

00:06:36.962 --> 00:06:41.816
dortn hobn shoyn gevart vagones oyf undz, m'hot onge- ongelodn di vagones

00:06:43.864 --> 00:06:47.016
onge⟨UNK⟩ mit mentshn, halb farkhaleshte mentshn, un m'hot zey,

00:06:47.016 --> 00:06:51.075
der der UNK der der ban hot zikh shoyn gerirt,

00:06:51.075 --> 00:06:54.337
hob ikh gezogt tsu mayn khaver, veyst, kum mir shpringen fun vagon.

00:06:54.462 --> 00:06:57.527
mir veln arayn arayn tantsn in vald, derbay mir UNK.

00:06:59.136 --> 00:07:03.652
s'iz shoyn geven nakht, un ikh hob der ershter aroysgeshprungen, un er hinter mir.

00:07:04.182 --> 00:07:05.948
mir zenen arayn in a kleynem veldele.

00:07:08.788 --> 00:07:14.553
un dortn hobn mir nit gevust vayter vu tsum geyn. hobn zikh avekgeleygt in a kust vu nit iz,

00:07:14.560 --> 00:07:20.966
un s'ongekumen di nakht shoyn, s'shoyn geven gor gor shpet in der nakht,

00:07:21.445 --> 00:07:22.941
undz hobn beyde ayngeshlofn.

00:07:23.419 --> 00:07:28.999
mit zikh hob ikh nokh gehat etlekhe kartofl in in in in dem sh- in di keshenes.

00:07:29.038 --> 00:07:36.705
di kartofl hobn mir hobn gehat genumen gefunen zeye- zayendik in lager fir, hobn di yidn

00:07:36.705 --> 00:07:46.701
di letste shoyn di letste hobn geshpirt az s'shoyn nito vos ontsuvern, hobn a groys hobn di yidn fun di la- fun fun di barakes aro- arayngekhapt zikh in dem kartofl lager fun kikh, un hobn im

00:07:47.449 --> 00:07:52.981
zikh arayngeshtupt zikh durkhn fentster un hobn gekhapt di kartofl. di daytshn hobn shoyn dan keyn zakh mit zey nit gekent makhn mit di,

00:07:52.981 --> 00:07:57.899
zey hobn shoyn dan sh- di postns hobn dan shoyn nit geshosn, zey hobn zikh shoyn a bisl baruikt,

00:07:57.899 --> 00:08:00.791
nor hobn di yidn hobn zikh ongekhapt mit a bisl kartofl, un ikh oykh,

00:08:01.270 --> 00:08:03.491
ikh in dem keshene hob ikh oykh gehat etlekhe kartofl.

00:08:05.083 --> 00:08:11.003
in di velder azoy in vald zenen zey mir zeyer tsu nits gekumen. mir hobn zikh beyde geteylt di kartofl di di

00:08:11.003 --> 00:08:13.869
di roye kartofl kedey tsu shtiln dem hunger.

00:08:14.500 --> 00:08:16.350
in der fri ven mir zenen beyde oyfgeshtanen,

00:08:16.508 --> 00:08:19.337
hobn mir nit gevust vu tsum vu zikh tsum kern, vu tsum geyn.

00:08:19.461 --> 00:08:28.938
zenen mir gelofn durkhn vald zukhn vos nit iz oyf a ort, efsher veln mir gefinen vu s'a shtibele oder vos nit iz. un grod hobn mir getrofn a oyfn veg hobn mir gezen a kleyninke shtibele.

00:08:30.666 --> 00:08:38.878
m'iz arayngelofn in shtibl, eyder m'hot undz arayngelofn in shtibl, iz fun shtibl aroysgelofn eyner der vekhter der der der vald vekhter,

00:08:39.745 --> 00:08:42.281
ongeton shoyn in tsiviler mitn revolver in der hant,

00:08:42.281 --> 00:08:45.746
er hot undz derzen, hot er ongehoybn tsu shisn oyf undz.

00:08:45.955 --> 00:08:49.661
un eyn koyl hot getrofn mayn khaver. im UNK dem dem yat.

00:08:49.701 --> 00:08:54.690
dos heyst bay lebn mir iz er gefaln. ikh bin tsugelo- ikh bin tsugegangen tsu, un der un der vekhter iz antlofn vayter.

00:08:55.033 --> 00:08:57.592
vayl er hot shoyn geshpirt az di amerikaner armey iz shoyn geven nit vayt.

00:08:58.830 --> 00:09:04.747
ikh bin tsugegangen tsu mayn khaver, ikh hob a kuk geton, ikh hob gezen di koyl hot im getrofn direkt glaykh in kop, er iz shoyn geven toyt.

00:09:05.091 --> 00:09:08.139
nu ikh hob keyn zakh nit gekent im helfn. ikh bin arayngegangen in shtibl,

00:09:08.550 --> 00:09:17.977
ikh bin geven farlayzikt, ikh bin geven shmutsik, ikh bin geven oysgematert. ikh hob kam kam zikh derkrokhn tsum tsum tsum a vinkl fun fun fun shti- fun tsimerl, ikh hob zikh avekgeleygt,

00:09:18.203 --> 00:09:24.676
un ikh hob zikh un ikh hob zikh a bisl opgerut. ikh bin ayngeshlofn.

00:09:26.623 --> 00:09:31.983
ikh hob fun zikh aruntergevorfn di aruntergevorfn di zakhn farshteyt zikh, un ikh bin ayngeshlofn azoy o. fardekt zikh mit a koldere

00:09:32.040 --> 00:09:37.181
vos iz dortn geven, un ay- un aroysge- un in der fri bin ikh oyfgeshtanen, hob ikh gehert a geroysh fun mashines.

00:09:37.322 --> 00:09:38.970
a ge- a geroysh fun tanken.

00:09:41.423 --> 00:09:47.188
ikh bin aroysgelofn a naketer durkhn tirl, a kuk tun ver vos dortn iz.

00:09:47.498 --> 00:09:52.251
un ikh gib a kuk ikh bin dokh naket, darf men onton zikh vos nit iz. oyfn oyfn vant iz gehangen a shinel

00:09:52.307 --> 00:09:56.013
a a shn- nit keyn shinel nor a a a fun a

00:09:58.315 --> 00:10:07.238
iz gehangen a fun fun dem vekhter. kentik hot der vekhter er iz antlofn, hot gehat, er iz geven avek- er iz geven a ofitsir kentik. hot er iber- zikh gikh ibergeton mit tsivil,

00:10:07.238 --> 00:10:09.660
un er hot gelozn hengen oyfn ha- oyfn vant

00:10:09.660 --> 00:10:20.279
zayn zayn zayn uniform. ikh hob gekhapt dem uniform oyf zikh mitn mitn shinel, un ikh hob aroysgelofn a kuk ton in vald vos far a royshn dortn, vos kumt dortn vos kumt dortn for.

00:10:20.573 --> 00:10:23.722
un dort hob ikh bamerkt az durkhn vald iz durkhgegangen tankes.

00:10:24.268 --> 00:10:25.665
un zey hobn mir bamerkt,

00:10:25.665 --> 00:10:29.949
s'hot fun unter fun eyn tank iz aroysgelo- aroysgelo- aroys getantst ofitsir, a kapitan,

00:10:30.242 --> 00:10:33.121
un gegebn a kuk oyf mir, oysgeshtelt di UNK tsu mir,

00:10:33.735 --> 00:10:36.074
er hot gezen mayn, in oyf uniform fun a daytsher,

00:10:36.553 --> 00:10:38.116
hot er gevolt mir shisn glaykh.

00:10:38.140 --> 00:10:41.846
hob ikh ongehoybn tsu shrayen, ikh bin eyn JUDE! shist nit!

00:10:42.105 --> 00:10:46.115
ikh bin eyn JUDE! WAS, zogt er, bist a JUDE? ikh bin, zogt er, oykh a yid!

00:10:47.455 --> 00:10:50.250
dos iz geven a kapitan fun der a- fun der amerikaner armey.

00:10:50.357 --> 00:10:51.645
ikh bin, zogt er, a yid.

00:10:51.645 --> 00:10:55.467
ikh vel dir helfn. kum, varf avek, zogt er, dem shmutsikn shinel,

00:10:55.467 --> 00:11:05.133
ikh vel dir gebn a amerikaner uniforme. un bist mistome hungerik, ikh vel dir on- on- on- onkormenen, ikh vel dir alts gebn. ze, mir veln dir nemen tsu zikh. er hot mir arayngezetst in tank,

00:11:06.507 --> 00:11:19.191
un m'hot mir gegebn esn. glaykh do hot zikh hot zikh gefunen hot zikh gefunen dortn a a sanitar tsi a dokter. m'hot mir gegebn glaykh opholn, ikh zol kumen tsu zikh, vayl ikh bin geven zeyer shvakh opgeshvakht oyf di fis, un m'hot mir avekgefirt in di shtetele Zumergarten.

00:11:20.074 --> 00:11:23.443
dortn bin ikh dortn hot men ayngeord- hot er ayngeordnt mir

00:11:23.466 --> 00:11:26.261
in a daytshisher mishpokhe, eltere mishpo- eltere mentshn,

00:11:26.352 --> 00:11:33.096
zey hobn mir gegebn a tsimerl a bazundern. zey hobn mit mir zikh zeyer gut bahandlt, zey hobn mir gegebn tsum esn, zey hobn mir gegebn

00:11:34.570 --> 00:11:48.218
ontsuton zikh farshteyt zikh un un un un un mir gegebn yedn tog iz gekumen di eltere froy un iberbin- iberbi- iberbindn di vundn vos ikh hob gehat oyf di oyf di fi- oyf di hent nokh fun fun fun mayn hengen.

00:11:48.691 --> 00:11:53.463
ikh ken nit zogn zey hobn UNK, zaynen do fun dest vegn daytsher daytshisher loytere mentshn velkhe ke- velkhe hobn geholfn.

00:11:53.622 --> 00:12:02.208
ikh veys nit vos far a tsil zey hobn gehat. zey hobn dertseylt az zeyer zun iz gefaln oyfn va- oyfn oyfn front oyfn oyfn mizrekh front in Rusland. az dem eyntsikn zun hobn zey farlorn.

00:12:02.208 --> 00:12:04.972
iz kentik az zey hobn derzen in mir efsher a mol dem zun zeyern.

00:12:05.400 --> 00:12:09.106
un in vinkl fun tsi- fun tsimer iz geshtanen zayne tsvey kabkes, tsvey

00:12:09.349 --> 00:12:13.514
shtek-shikh. hot zi mir geozgt, her tsu, liber froynt,

00:12:13.514 --> 00:12:22.657
ale, du bist eyn, du bist a balebos in in dem tsimer, ober di shtek-shikh zolstu nit tshepenen. zogt er, s'a ondenkung far undzer gefalenem undzern, bay undz iz es a min traditsye

00:12:22.900 --> 00:12:26.201
tsu haltn di shtek-shikh. ikh hob di shtek-shikh nit tsu- zikh tsugerirt tsu zey.

00:12:28.620 --> 00:12:33.744
un ikh hob gelebt bay zey in dem tsimer hob ikh gelebt a lange lengere tsayt, a por monatn tsayt in di.

00:12:34.037 --> 00:12:47.278
fun dortn dortn in dem in di zelbe shtetl hobn gelebt nokh oykh fa- fa- bafrayte yidn. ikh hob zikh mit zey ba- mit zey bakent un mir hobn bashlosn tsu forn, mir hobn gehert az in Minkhn gefinen zikh kazarmes un in di kazarmes gefinen zikh yidn,

00:12:47.689 --> 00:12:50.079
tsunoyfgezamlte yidn fun farsheydene lagern,

00:12:50.338 --> 00:12:58.837
un dortn fun dortn vet men vet men kenen onforn tsurik aheym in undzer foterland, in Lite.

00:13:00.075 --> 00:13:03.100
in Minkhn zenen mir geven a kurtse tsayt.

00:13:03.175 --> 00:13:09.075
m'hot undz dortn zeyer gut gegebn esn, m'hot undz ongeton, di amerikaner hobn zikh zeyer gut tsu undz batsoygn,

00:13:09.075 --> 00:13:14.950
un yedn tog flegn mir krign shokolad, fleg krign farsheydene produktn,

00:13:14.950 --> 00:13:18.850
biz, far undz iz geven a groyse zakh, vayle gevezn gemutshete mentshn fun lager.

00:13:18.850 --> 00:13:23.425
hob ikh zikh gikh a bisl gekumen tsu zikh, zikh a bisl shoyn far- far- bapravet azoy tsu zogn.

00:13:24.595 --> 00:13:30.410
un emesn zenen gekumen tsu forn dortn forshteyer fun Yisroel, fun Erets-Yisroel.

00:13:30.906 --> 00:13:42.020
un zey ongehoybn tsum onagatirn, zogn, "khevre, yidishe khevre, ir darft forn in eygene land. vu fort ir aheym? vu fort ir? iz es ayere heym? ir hot dortn dokh farlorn ayere eltern, farlorn ayere ayere

00:13:42.060 --> 00:13:44.335
f- bakante, ayere fraynt, ayere kroyvim.

00:13:44.335 --> 00:13:47.099
kumt tsu forn mit undz in Erets-Yisroel, dortn

00:13:47.292 --> 00:13:50.340
dortn vet vet keyn lagern shoyn mer nit zayn far aykh."

00:13:51.021 --> 00:14:00.938
nu ikh bin nokh dan geven in gantsn nayntsn yor. ikh hob nokh alts gelebt mitn gayst fun dem sovetishn azoy tsu zogn umpartizanishn gayst.

00:14:01.467 --> 00:14:02.811
vos heyst, ikh hob dokh

00:14:03.289 --> 00:14:14.491
fun dest vegn geven, oyf mir hot dokh alts gevust az ikh darf zayn in der in der organizatsye in der partizanisher organizatsye fun geto, un der der un der unternemen in in der aktiver unternemen in zayn arbet hot mir alts getsoygn

00:14:14.491 --> 00:14:16.631
tsu tsu dortn in shtot in Kovne.

00:14:16.705 --> 00:14:25.879
un mir hobn zikh ikh hob dortn getrofn Dime Galpe- Dime Gelpern, ikh hob getrofn dortn

00:14:27.673 --> 00:14:35.213
Grinbergn, oykh a un- a aktiver unternemer fun fun der organizatsye fun der fun der un-

00:14:35.213 --> 00:14:37.303
di partizanisher geto organizatsye.

00:14:41.595 --> 00:14:45.672
ikh hob getrofn dortn nokh azelkhe khevre velkhe, un mir hobn bashlosn tsu forn aheym.

00:14:46.725 --> 00:14:51.899
yedn tog zenen gekumen tsu forn ruzevikes, m'hot undz arayngezetst in di in di in di last oyto- last-oytos,

00:14:51.923 --> 00:14:54.195
un m'hot undz gefirt tsum grenets tsu Khelmits.

00:14:54.353 --> 00:14:58.599
dortn iz geven der grenets tsvishn di amerikaner un di sovetn, un sovetishe armey.

00:15:00.411 --> 00:15:02.109
ven m'hot undz gebrakht in Khelmits,

00:15:03.347 --> 00:15:05.332
hot men undz glaykh oyfn grenets

00:15:05.710 --> 00:15:10.918
hobn di sovetishe soldatn undz glaykh tsugenumen azoy tsu zogn tsu zikh, un geheysn in der ershter rey geyn in bod.

00:15:11.481 --> 00:15:17.825
un undzer, mir hobn gehat, ikh hob gehat bay zikh a ruk-zak hob ikh dortn gehat bay zikh azelkhe zakhn fun di daytshn vos ikh hob fun zey gekrogn a matone dortn a

00:15:17.829 --> 00:15:20.904
a por hoyzn iberike, a por shikh hobn zey mir gegebn dortn,

00:15:20.904 --> 00:15:23.479
nokh UNK ikh gedenk shoyn nit velkhe zakhn,

00:15:23.479 --> 00:15:25.829
velkhe zenen geven in yener tsayt a groyser vert.

00:15:25.960 --> 00:15:31.850
hobn mir gehey- hobn zey geheysn di rusishe soldatn hobn undz gezogt az mir zoln iberlozn lebn ban lebn

00:15:31.910 --> 00:15:34.285
lebn dem bod iberlozn undzere rukzek,

00:15:34.285 --> 00:15:38.262
un mir veln arayngeyn in bod, un geye- aroysgeyendik fun tsurik veln mir krign demolts tsurik di zakhn.

00:15:38.262 --> 00:15:40.562
mir zenen arayn in bod, un mir hobn zikh oysgebodn,

00:15:40.562 --> 00:15:46.262
mir geyen aroys fun bod, mir gebn a kuk do, undzere rukzek zenen shoyn nito. farfaln gevorn undzere ale zakhn.

00:15:46.262 --> 00:15:49.887
ot dos hobn undz ge- azoy hobn undz getrofn di sovetishe soldatn.

00:15:50.597 --> 00:15:53.190
hob ikh glaykh farshtanen vu mir zenen shoyn arayngefaln.

00:15:53.972 --> 00:15:58.438
nor un ikh hob alts nokh getrakht az fun dest vegn es vet nokh kumen di tsayt az kumen azoy tsu zogn

00:15:59.018 --> 00:16:02.977
fun dest vegn vet men zikh farrekhenen mit di mentshn velkhe zenen geven in lager un m'vet

00:16:03.304 --> 00:16:07.570
un UNK mit di velkhe zenen hobn zikh untergenumen in di farsheydene

00:16:07.570 --> 00:16:13.845
partizanishe bavegungen un azoy vayter. efsher vet efsher vet men undzer mit undz di unter⟨UNK⟩ zey zey bahandlen.

00:16:14.425 --> 00:16:20.038
hobn mir bashlosn geyn tsu fus aheym.

00:16:21.124 --> 00:16:26.838
m'hot undz gevolt mobilizirn in otryadn arayntsugeyn arayntsugebn in in di rusishe armey,

00:16:27.165 --> 00:16:33.014
oder ikh veys nit vu m'zogn vu m'hot undz gevolt, oder m'hot undz gevolt dortn farpshe- haltn avekfirn in Sibir,

00:16:33.055 --> 00:16:35.372
velkhe derfar vos vos mir zenen geven in di lagern.

00:16:35.372 --> 00:16:41.857
nor ikh bin tsu in di otryadn nit gegangen, mir hobn zikh opgeteylt a bazundere grupe, mir zenen gegangen tsu fus oyf tsu Kovne.

00:16:42.673 --> 00:16:49.197
farshteyt zikh, tsu fus hobn mir nit gekent dergeyn azoy vayt. mir zenen geforn, teyl zenen mir teylvay- teylvayz zenen mir geforn, teyl zenen mir gegangen tsu fus,

00:16:49.255 --> 00:16:51.898
mit mir iz gegangen Belinke Kremerman,

00:16:52.191 --> 00:16:55.560
oykh a UNK, a untererdisher, mit zayn shvoger.

00:16:55.785 --> 00:16:57.500
er iz gegangen zukhn zayn froy.

00:16:57.827 --> 00:17:02.073
ikh bin gegangen zukhn ke- nor mayne fraynt. ikh hob gevust az mayn gantse mishpokhe iz umgekumen.

00:17:03.042 --> 00:17:04.690
mir zenen gegangen biz Berlin,

00:17:05.556 --> 00:17:10.309
do geforn nit gegangen, nor oykh geforn farshteyt zikh, in Berlin hobn mir getrofn nokh khaveyrim.

00:17:10.855 --> 00:17:13.262
a teyl zey hobn shoyn gevust dem gantsn

00:17:14.027 --> 00:17:17.077
dem gantsn rezhim fun dem sovetisher sovetisher rezhim,

00:17:17.077 --> 00:17:24.027
hobn zey zikh a nit gekert in Kov- nit umgekert Kovne, zenen geblibn arbetn in Berlin dortn, bay eynem a general Marshak, dortn geven eyner Marshak er hot

00:17:24.027 --> 00:17:27.952
oyf- oyfgenumen bay zikh yidn tsu arbetn in zayn in zayn teyl.

00:17:28.540 --> 00:17:31.436
nor ikh bin mit di khevre gekumen tsurik in Kovne.

00:17:31.729 --> 00:17:41.443
in Kovne farshteyt zikh hob gevolt ikh a kuk ton vu ikh leb, vu iz undzer gevezener gas, mir hobn gelebt oyf Vayse gas, oyf Yamner gas, nokh oyf andere gasn, hob ikh a kuk geton, di shtot iz pust,

00:17:41.753 --> 00:17:45.780
mentshn zenen andere, groy in gantsn.

00:17:46.292 --> 00:17:54.017
ikh hob zikh forgeshtelt az m'vet undz oyfnemen a bisl andersh. ikh hob gedarft aroysnemen a pasport khotshabe, ober m'hot keyn pasport nit gegebn mit di mentshn velkhe zenen gekumen, di

00:17:54.017 --> 00:17:58.976
yidn velkhe zenen gekumen fun di lagern hot men UNK gehaltn far far mentshn fun tsveytn sort.

00:17:59.269 --> 00:18:03.026
m'hot undz m'hot undz UNK pasn pa- keyn pasn nit gevolt aroysgebn.

00:18:03.640 --> 00:18:08.933
un s'geven a dike di groysedike diskriminatsye fun di fun di mentshn.

00:18:10.238 --> 00:18:15.699
ikh hob getrofn mayne khaveyrim velkhe zenen gekumen fun partizanik- fun partizanishe bavegung. ikh hob getrofn dortn Shimke Blokh,

00:18:16.077 --> 00:18:25.014
ikh hob getrofn Meyske Mutshelis, Nekhemke Englin, Leyzerke Zilber,

00:18:27.130 --> 00:18:29.278
ikh bin arayn tsu zey in shtub, zey hobn mir dertseylt

00:18:29.278 --> 00:18:36.894
az der der rezhim iz do aza min der sovetisher rezhim iz nit geneygt tsu di yidn velkhe zenen geven in di lagern.

00:18:40.208 --> 00:18:44.167
vayter, hob ikh zikh bakent mit eyn a froy,

00:18:44.730 --> 00:18:47.930
velkhe hot mir geratn tsu forn in Vilne, zi vet mir araynnemen mit der arbet.

00:18:48.207 --> 00:18:52.909
ire ire bakanter, guter bakanter, Shperling iz geven do a

00:18:53.185 --> 00:18:55.524
onfirer fun a aptey- fun apteyke-sklad,

00:18:55.547 --> 00:19:01.599
fun apteykn volt ikh gezogt UNK vi azoy heyst dos,

00:19:03.057 --> 00:19:08.670
farvaltung, un bay im, ikh hob gekrogn fun ir a tsetele tsu im, er zol mir araynnemen in der arbet.

00:19:08.963 --> 00:19:10.459
ikh bin arayngeforn in Vilne,

00:19:11.224 --> 00:19:18.576
ikh bin arayn tsu im in shtub. er hot zikh zeyer interesirt, er hot zikh zeyer shtark interesirt vegn di yidn velkhe zenen geven in lager. ikh hob im dertseylt vegn zikh, vegn mayne eltern,

00:19:18.683 --> 00:19:22.409
un er hot mir gegeb- forgeleygt tsu arbetn im, er hot mir gegebn

00:19:22.409 --> 00:19:31.889
a li- halb litviner karteshke iz dan geven in Ko- in in yener tsayt nokhn krig. dos heyst m'hot gekent far a halb litviner karteshke flegt men zikh shoyn kenen kam kam durkhlebn.

00:19:32.790 --> 00:19:38.116
un er hot mir bazorgn an ort vu tsum vu tsu vu tsum shlofn. tsu zikh in shtub hot er mir nit genumen. er hot mir gegebn an ort in zayn

00:19:38.325 --> 00:19:41.002
in zayn UNK, heyst in zayn

00:19:42.223 --> 00:19:47.316
algemeynem va- voynung, ye, az dortn zol ikh ibernekhtikn.

00:19:42.998 --> 00:19:44.573
algemeynem voynung.

00:19:47.316 --> 00:19:53.895
un ikh hob bashlosn az far mir iz dortn keyn ort nit, ikh vil zikh prubirn aleyn on a- aynordenen on keyn hilf.

00:19:55.386 --> 00:19:59.987
nu in Vilne hob ikh getrofn bakante,

00:20:02.220 --> 00:20:05.791
velkhe hobn mir, iz geven iz geven di familye Silkiner,

00:20:06.878 --> 00:20:10.955
Shmuel un Khave Silkiner, velkhe hobn mir arayngenumen tsu zikh.

00:20:14.067 --> 00:20:16.963
un zey hobn mir bashlosn oykh tsu mir helfn.

00:20:17.188 --> 00:20:18.802
ikh fleg dortn a mol opesn,

00:20:18.808 --> 00:20:28.015
oystrinken a gloz tey mit a mit a shtikl mit a mit a konfekt flegt men flegt men oyf broyt iz dan geven oyf oyfn oyf di oyf a karteshke iz geven zeyer shver.

00:20:28.191 --> 00:20:31.408
un dortn flegn zikh kumen a yidishe khevre, yidishe meydlekh,

00:20:31.414 --> 00:20:33.264
m'fleg zikh mit zey bakanen,

00:20:33.372 --> 00:20:36.878
un un eyn mol hot men mir forgeleygt

00:20:36.878 --> 00:20:42.900
di khaver Silkiner, zogt zi, "vos, s'dokh nit takhles, m'darf zen vos tsu hobn efsher zen zen tsum arbetn.

00:20:43.075 --> 00:20:47.700
der foter iz dokh geven a me- mebl-shiker, iz dokh geven a a zeyer guter meblesher, a guter

00:20:47.712 --> 00:20:52.612
mebler mebls-arbeter, efsher vestu oykh zikh kenen mit dem farnemen. kum makh di ershte profit tsu makhn.

00:20:52.612 --> 00:20:54.512
nem, ot iz bay mir iz do a matrats,

00:20:54.512 --> 00:20:58.287
vu ikh vu ikh shlof, er iz a gelekherter, shoyn in gantsn mit a mit tife grub,

00:20:58.287 --> 00:21:00.618
efsher, prubir efsher vestu kenen vos iz makhn fun im.

00:21:00.945 --> 00:21:03.251
efsher vestu kenen im farrikhtn, makhn remont."

00:21:03.426 --> 00:21:08.013
ikh hob genumen genumen di dreystkeyt un ikh hob genumen dem matrats, ikh hob im ikh hob im oysgeshnitn dortn di sh- di

00:21:08.013 --> 00:21:10.913
du shpongatn mit di pruzhines, m'hot zey avekgeshtelt alts oyf an ort,

00:21:10.913 --> 00:21:13.238
ikh hob im batsoygn mit di mit a shtik shtof aza min,

00:21:13.238 --> 00:21:17.863
un s'gevorn a vunderbarer matrats. trakht ikh, oy, ikh bin dokh shoyn bald a a shpetsyalist, ikh ken shoyn bald arbetn.

00:21:18.630 --> 00:21:24.328
nu, fun do, un dos iz geven di ershte arbet mayne, der matrats fun Silkinern, dos gedenk ikh biz hayntikn tog.

00:21:25.768 --> 00:21:32.768
nu vayter bin ikh sof kol sof hob ikh gef- getrofn zikh mit a eynem a direktor vos fun fun a kambinat,

00:21:32.768 --> 00:21:37.843
velkher hot mir forgeleygt aleyn, az er hot a lokal tsum arbetn, tsu efenen a varshtat.

00:21:37.881 --> 00:21:46.232
a varshtat fun veykhe meb- fun remont fun veykhe mebl. oyf Gortshe gas iz dos geven. dortn iz geven mit a groyse vitrine,

00:21:49.005 --> 00:21:57.228
un dortn hot er mir tsugezogt er vet mir aynordenen, mir zoln nemen di initsyativ tsu makhn, in der tsayt iz dokh geven geven in yener tsayt iz geven zeyer veynik azelkhene varshtatn fun veykhe mebl,

00:21:57.228 --> 00:21:59.228
zogt er, vest kenen arbetn, vest kenen fardinen.

00:21:59.228 --> 00:22:04.131
nor aleyn iz er geven a bisl rizikalish, ikh hob es nit farshtanen vi azoy kenen men es ton.

00:22:04.131 --> 00:22:08.169
hob ikh genumen tsu zikh eynem Ratshkovitshn, an alter Ratshkovitsh, a shloser aleyn fun fakh,

00:22:08.800 --> 00:22:12.742
er hot vegn tapetsireray vegn di arbet fun veykhe mebl keyn zakh nit gevust.

00:22:12.748 --> 00:22:14.868
nor ikh hob gezogt, veystu vos, ikh vel dir oyslernen.

00:22:15.128 --> 00:22:16.776
khotsh ikh hob aleyn veynik vos gekent.

00:22:17.490 --> 00:22:22.406
ikh vel dir oyslernen, mir veln arbetn tsuzamen. mir hobn gearbet, un take azoy hobn mir gearbet tsuzamen, lange yorn.

00:22:22.406 --> 00:22:24.217
gearbet alts fun fun veykhe mebl.

00:22:25.303 --> 00:22:31.484
nu di gantse troym fun mayn fun mayn lebn iz geven fun dest vegn nit keyn tsu zayn keyn te-

00:22:31.484 --> 00:22:35.059
tapetsirer, nit zayn keyn mebl arbeter. ikh hob UNK getrakht di gantse tsayt

00:22:35.059 --> 00:22:39.134
oder arbetn, ikh hob a neygung tsu literatur, ikh fleg shraybn,

00:22:39.134 --> 00:22:43.484
ikh hob gehat a neygung tsu kunst,

00:22:43.484 --> 00:22:51.774
un ikh bin avek avek lernen in ovnt in ovnter shu- kunst-shul, vu ikh hob ir geendikt.

00:22:52.017 --> 00:23:02.760
in etlekhe un fuftsikstn yor dakht zikh iz es geven. un fun dortn bin ikh aroys als spetsyalist als internalist, als dekorator, kinstler dekorator.

00:23:04.572 --> 00:23:07.299
nu mayn mir hot men shoyn gekent in shtot,

00:23:09.246 --> 00:23:19.258
m'hot mir gegebn arbet in ministorn kabinet, hot men mir arayngenumen als spetsyalist, ikh zol helfn dortn

00:23:19.258 --> 00:23:22.275
oy- oyf formen azoy tsu zogn dem

00:23:22.333 --> 00:23:29.083
dem interyer UNK, ikh hob zeyer groy- ikh hob gearbet bay bay Shumans- Shumanskesn, bay bay Shnietskusn, in Saka,

00:23:29.083 --> 00:23:34.248
in zeyere in zeyere te- in zeyere kabinetn.

00:23:34.248 --> 00:23:38.873
UNK flegt men boyen, in yener tsayt flegn zey boyen in in in un

00:23:38.873 --> 00:23:47.073
in Palangen farsheydene ru-hayzer, fleg ikh kumen tsu forn dortn, fleg ikh makhn gantsn fun groyser arbet.

00:23:47.417 --> 00:23:57.401
un do hot pasirt oyf aza min arbet vu ikh hob gearbet, ven mir hobn geboyt oyf Lako oyf Lako gas, in UNK,

00:23:57.660 --> 00:24:05.366
hot men tsum tsvantsikstn yuli gedarft endikn a naye oysgeboyte hoyz.

00:24:05.389 --> 00:24:13.129
m'hot gedarft, dos iz geven in akhtsikstn yor, m'hot gevart oyf Brezhevn. er hot gedarft kumen tsu forn in tsu gast.

00:24:14.181 --> 00:24:21.966
ot di hoyz hot gerufn hot zikh ongerufn di Brezhev hoyz. un mir hot men dortn genumen als dekorator, ikh zol do forn un ikh zol dortn in ordenung brengen alts

00:24:21.966 --> 00:24:24.688
ineveynik dem gantsn interyer, dem ineveynikstn interyer.

00:24:25.268 --> 00:24:27.135
ikh bin arayngefaln tsu der arbet dortn,

00:24:27.546 --> 00:24:33.650
di arbet iz geven zeyer a shvere, mir flegn arbetn tog un un afile nekht. ikh hob zikh getrofn mit farsheydene kinstler velkhe hobn mir geholfn,

00:24:33.671 --> 00:24:38.371
mit mit di nemen gedenk ikh nit ⟨itst⟩.

00:24:39.448 --> 00:24:43.653
Shupalis iz geven mayner a mayner a mitarbeter in undzer brigade fun dem kunst-arbeter

00:24:43.653 --> 00:24:47.903
UNK. s'geven dortn nokh azelkhe

00:24:47.903 --> 00:24:57.003
Urbanas, oykh dortn geven a, er hot hot dortn durkhgemakht farsheydene farsheydene kinstlerishe arbet.

00:24:57.769 --> 00:24:59.889
eyn mol hot er mir gezogt, Urbanas, tsu mir.

00:25:00.148 --> 00:25:04.327
Geguzhinskis, vi kenstu arbetn in azelkhene badingungen?

00:25:05.278 --> 00:25:12.350
durkh aza min kurtser tsayt oyftsuboyen aza min hoyf, a tsvey etazhn hoyz, mit mit mit mit vifl dortn e- etlekhe un tsvantsik tsimern, mit mit

00:25:12.499 --> 00:25:16.474
mit mit azelkh- sh- mit a sheynem mit kikhn farsheydene, mit mit a baseyn, mit

00:25:16.474 --> 00:25:19.524
mit vanes, mit far doktoyrim ko- tsimern,

00:25:19.593 --> 00:25:25.975
mit ale luks un ale azelkhene zakhn vos iz in Viln- in gants Viln- in Vil- in Rotn- in Ratn-Farband iz dos nito.

00:25:25.981 --> 00:25:29.206
un durkh aza min kurtser tsayt, zogt er, zolst kumen yedn tog, zolst geyn ot o di

00:25:29.206 --> 00:25:34.806
di di minist- minister iz geblibn der Shimo- der Shinetski iz shoyn geven geshtorbn dan.

00:25:34.823 --> 00:25:41.401
es kumen tsu geyn, zogt er, di ale natshalstve ibern kop un zey lozn dir nit arbetn, yeder yeder eyntsikster zogt zayne zogt dir direktivn.

00:25:41.408 --> 00:25:45.317
ikh, zogt er, ken shoyn mer nit arbetn. ikh vel oder ikh vel krign, zogt er, a ilfakt, oder a insut.

00:25:45.458 --> 00:25:48.591
un azoy hot pasirt. ikh hob zikh fun der arbet nit opgelozn,

00:25:48.698 --> 00:25:55.998
un ikh hob der- der- dertsoygn di arbet bizn bizn tog, bizn tsvantsikstn yuli. di arbet iz geven fartik, UNK.

00:25:56.680 --> 00:26:02.091
ikh hob ongeklungen dem shef maynem, yener iz geven UNK, hot gearbet der shef, UNK, ikh hob im ongeklungen,

00:26:02.637 --> 00:26:05.162
ikh hob im gedarft yedn t- yedn tog ibergebn

00:26:06.602 --> 00:26:09.346
dem raport, vi di arbet gefirt vert vert oysgefirt.

00:26:10.990 --> 00:26:17.328
kling ikh im on, un ikh UNK iz geven in kabinet un s'geven di sekretarshe.

00:26:17.470 --> 00:26:24.349
zog ikh tsu ir, git iber UNK az di arbet iz fartik, Geguzhinski hot geklungen az er er iz hot oysgefirt di arbet bizn sof.

00:26:26.059 --> 00:26:30.170
zogt zi, eyn minut, ot bald ot iz er arayn in kabinet. ikh vel ir shoyn zogn.

00:26:31.206 --> 00:26:37.224
s'avek iber a minut, zogt ent- entfert zi tsu mir, er vil mit dir nit reydn.

00:26:37.804 --> 00:26:41.172
er iz farnumen. mit yidn, zogt er, hob ikh UNK tsum ton.

00:26:42.765 --> 00:26:48.378
mir iz gevorn, ikh hob gehert di reyd, iz mir gevorn shlekht. ikh bin geshtanen baym telefon bay mir in kabinet,

00:26:48.385 --> 00:26:51.442
un ikh hob aro- s'aruntergefaln bay mir di trubke fun hant,

00:26:51.442 --> 00:26:58.792
un ikh bin aruntergefaln avek ni- ikh hob zikh nit gekent oyf. mir s'hot zikh zeyer shtark fardrosn, ikh hob arayngeleygt azoy fil arbet in dem un do mit a yidn vil er shoyn nit reydn.

00:26:58.792 --> 00:27:03.167
meglekh er iz geven shtark nervirt, meglekh er iz geven, ober er hot dermont er iz

00:27:03.181 --> 00:27:06.688
az mayn mayn natsyonal dos heyst mayn mayn mayn mayn shtamung,

00:27:06.913 --> 00:27:08.561
hot mir zeyer shtark fardrosn,

00:27:08.820 --> 00:27:13.336
un ikh hob genumen, ikh hob zikh arayngezetst in mayn mashin, ikh hob gehat aza mashin,

00:27:13.562 --> 00:27:19.158
an eygene mashin, a Zhigoli numer dray. un gekumen tsu forn aheym.

00:27:20.802 --> 00:27:22.568
un s'mir gevorn zeyer shlekht,

00:27:22.624 --> 00:27:25.689
ikh hob zikh geleygt shlofn. oyf morgn in der fri bin ikh oyfgeshtanen

00:27:26.100 --> 00:27:30.481
un gevorn paralizirt. bay mir iz paralizirt gevorn di linke hant un di linke fus.

00:27:31.922 --> 00:27:34.737
nu men hot mir arayngeleygt glaykh in shpitol.

00:27:34.737 --> 00:27:42.559
ot der zelber Yane-Noyekh hot geton far mir a groyse toyve, er hot mir genumen loyt zayn onvayzung tsu heyln in di Shpets shpitol.

00:27:42.559 --> 00:27:45.467
in a palate a bazundere palate hot men mir dortn geheylt.

00:27:46.232 --> 00:27:52.200
un er iz gekumen tsu mir eyn mol eyn mol tsu gast a kuk ton vi ikh leb. vayl er hot farshtanen dem, er hot farshtanen az er iz shuldik in dem.

00:27:52.408 --> 00:27:57.110
vayl bay mir iz geven a guter dokter Shutrauskes,

00:27:58.028 --> 00:28:02.865
Stolpinyenye velkhe hot mir zeyer fil geholfn. zi hot zikh genumen tsu mir punkt vi a muter,

00:28:03.546 --> 00:28:07.843
un zi hot gezogt zi vet mir oysheyln, zi vet makhn fun mir a mentshn. un take azoy iz geven.

00:28:08.406 --> 00:28:11.660
ikh hob zikh avekgeshtelt oyf di fis, ikh hob ongehoybn makhn di ershte trit,

00:28:14.700 --> 00:28:15.524
UNK
